### Actual Output:
@startuml marmarek_qubes-app-u2f
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

package "Browser VM" {
  rectangle "Web Browser" as Browser
  rectangle "CTAP Client" as Client
  rectangle "HID Emulator" as HIDEmulator
  rectangle "Qrexec Client" as QrexecClient
}

package "sys-usb VM" {
  rectangle "CTAP Proxy" as Proxy
  rectangle "Qrexec Server" as QrexecServer
  rectangle "USB Stack" as USBStack
  rectangle "Physical Token" as Token
}

package "Qubes OS" {
  rectangle "Qrexec Policy" as Policy
}

Browser --> Client : CTAP Requests
Client --> HIDEmulator : HID Emulation
HIDEmulator --> QrexecClient : Forward Requests
QrexecClient --> QrexecServer : Secure IPC
QrexecServer --> Proxy : Process Requests
Proxy --> USBStack : USB Commands
USBStack --> Token : Physical Access

Policy --> QrexecClient : Access Control
Policy --> QrexecServer : Access Control

note right of Token
  CTAP1/U2F and CTAP2 protocols
end note
@enduml